&lt;p&gt;As a Territory Manager at Dreem Health, you’ll be out in the field every day, building trusted relationships with physicians, specialists, and clinics to drive referrals to our digital sleep clinic. You’ll promote our life-changing sleep care services, especially for patients with sleep apnea, by educating providers, organizing lunch &amp;amp; learns, and creating awareness across your territory. You&#39;ll track referral activity, share insights with internal teams, and play a hands-on role in shaping how we grow. This is a high-impact opportunity for someone who thrives on connection, loves being on the go, and wants to be part of a mission-driven team transforming access to care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Sunrise Group, we work on a problem that affects millions: poor sleep and untreated sleep disorders. Our mission is to make diagnosis and care easier to access, and we’re proud of the experience we provide to patients. We feel responsible for making it better every day. If you’re looking for the autonomy to take ownership of your work, make an impact, and be part of a team where ideas move fast and everyone has a voice -&amp;nbsp; this role is for you!&lt;/p&gt;
