&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2+&amp;nbsp;years&amp;nbsp;in&amp;nbsp;healthcare,&amp;nbsp;either&amp;nbsp;in&amp;nbsp;partnerships,&amp;nbsp;provider&amp;nbsp;relations,&amp;nbsp;or&amp;nbsp;sales&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree in Business, Healthcare Administration, or related field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Valid Driver&#39;s License and clean driving record&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of healthcare referral processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with CRM systems (we use Hubspot) and data reporting tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A genuine passion for improving healthcare access and patient outcomes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
