&lt;li&gt;Existing network of primary care providers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of sleep health, mainly sleep apnea&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional relationship-building and communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strategic and entrepreneurial approach to territory management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Adaptability in a fast-growing healthcare and tech environment&lt;/li&gt;
