&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This is a non-clinical, operational role that partners closely with Sleep Technologists during the transition from treatment setup to long-term resupply. Once patients enter the resupply phase, you will coordinate follow-up, execution, and documentation to ensure a smooth and reliable experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work within a tech-enabled, AI-supported care environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with clinical, billing, and operations teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help track engagement and reorder metrics while contributing to a scalable operational foundation inside a fast-growing digital sleep clinic.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute timely and proactive resupply outreach&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow structured retention workflows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain accurate reorder tracking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate clearly and compassionately with patients&l
